metadata.name: Elite Foxes Club
metadata.description: The Elite Foxes is a collection of 1260 unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain- the NFT that’s all about it’s community— Owning an Elite Fox will be used as your club membership card, granting you access to members-only benefits. Join the Elite Fox community and connect with like minded visionaries that all want to take over the Metaverse.
